Hugo Broos host his first media as Bafana Bafana's new coach. The Belgian comes into a national team low on confidence, after failing to qualify for the 2021 Africa Cup of Nations. * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - New Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos is briefing the media on Wednesday. Broos comes into a national team low on confidence after failing to qualify for the 2021 Africa Cup of Nations. READ: Broos signs five-year contract with SA His immediate goal will be to qualify for the 2022 FIFA World Cup in Qatar.